items.title: Libya's army chief killed in air crash in Turkey
items.description: Signal was earlier lost with a jet that took off from Ankara with Gen Mohammed Ali Ahmed al-Haddad and four others on board.

items.title: Trump travelled on Epstein's plane more than previously thought, prosecutor says
items.description: The US president has long denied any wrongdoing in relation to late convicted sex offender Jeffrey Epstein.

items.title: Ukraine loses embattled eastern town
items.description: The capture of Siversk brings Russia closer to the last remaining "fortress belt" cities still in Ukrainian hands in the Donetsk region.

items.title: US economy grows at fastest pace in two years
items.description: Strong consumer spending helps the US economy grow at a faster rate than expected.

items.title: Gunmen abduct 28 Muslim travellers in central Nigeria
items.description: The victims, including women and children, were ambushed on their way to a religious festival.
